===EXERCISE 1 ===
Write a program that asks the user to type an [[w:Integer|integer]] and writes "YOU WIN" if the value is between 56 and 78 (both included). In the other case it writes "YOU LOSE". 
{{solution|title=Solution|text=
<source lang=cpp>
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
	int i;
	cout << "Type a number between 58 and 73: " << endl;
	cin >> i;
	if (i>=58 && i<=78)
	{
		cout << "YOU WIN" << endl;
	} 
	else 
	{			
		cout << "YOU LOSE" << endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
