== Unknown artist, unknown album ==

Some have complained of lots of songs having unknown artist and unknown album. That problem has been tentatively tracked down to a [[Wikipedia:Universal Serial Bus|USB]] cable that truncates the files. Since the [[Wikipedia:ID3|ID3]] tags are at the end of the files, those could easily be missing if the last 1Kb of the file is truncated. Try another cable, and see if that fixes the problem.

{{BookCat}}

